peopleAlsoAsk.question: Is there a market for old postage stamps?
peopleAlsoAsk.snippet: In truth, the majority of stamps are actually worth very little because they are issued in huge quantities. However, if you are lucky enough to own a collection of rare stamps which are in good condition it might be a very valuable asset.
